        <dc:creator><![CDATA[juanma]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Hi <a class="mention" href="https://community.frontity.org/u/asim">@asim</a>,</p>
<p>Welcome to the Community!</p>
<p>Are you launching <code>npx frontity dev</code> from inside a frontity project (the folder created when you did <code>npx frontity create your-project</code>)?</p>
<p>Try to do the whole process (create a project, get inside the folder, launch dev server) from the beginning. Here you have a <a href="https://docs.frontity.org/getting-started/quick-start-guide">Quick start guide</a> of how to do it</p>
<p>What are you planning to do with Frontity?</p>
